"msg":"push"},{"pid":"bc21c5cffd89f52a072090a7e332536cdd6dd6d2","tid":1417760,"uid":20834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:53:45.000Z","msg":"推！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得民間記者唔可以預設立場<br />\n好易比人扣帽子<br />\n而家個淺藍深藍個個都睇緊紅媒 <br />\n民間記者會應該以中立人角色 <br />\n客觀咁重點報道返一啲大是大非 全世界都覺得錯既野 去攻破政府<br />\n彌補返紅媒主導既呢個盲點 等多啲人知 政府/警隊做左啲咩對唔住市民 質疑政府<br />\n<br />\n唔應該用示威者身份去講行動原則 <br />\notherwise 又會變左大台<br />\n<br />\n呢步棋唔易行 亦都唔可以行錯"},{"pid":"8b39b0813f22b041ea18523254d19b4ba4d4c4b5","tid":1417760,"uid":241844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:06:57.000Z","msg":"繼續努力 加油"},{"pid":"b08a6a79c19e653ef7c03902c19bafb3d8bfdb00","tid":1417760,"uid":15102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:09:59.000Z","msg":"希望睇到 我都覺得講完某啲事件 可以播10-15秒片俾大家睇"},{"pid":"0859692ded2949e3141fa4c2b671699824c62a71","tid":1417760,"uid":298938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:14:40.000Z","msg":"推!!!"},{"pid":"b13a183a84af01effd0fc189e5f8fbb60303aa7a","tid":1417760,"uid":37686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:17:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cc9edcb9776f43c3420abd7eb40a5741b20936fc","tid":1417760,"uid":296923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:21:55.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"396e2b7eb7d386c95e14eaf76d5e38b169e0dfd8","tid":1417760,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:43:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0281dbef042043d16785de253763baafd6e92678","tid":1417760,"uid":100714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:48:30.000Z","msg":"大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a648721dee66b6b182f9cabb1b268e6df7ed6e26","tid":1417760,"uid":160268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:48:44.000Z","msg":"留名睇連登仔 唔聽意見<br />\n<br />\n覺得自已係前線 就一日一日惡過紅衛兵<br />\n<br />\n琴晚已經不停係街批鬥/處決咗好多異見市民"}]}